msgstr "# triton.language.dot"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Linear_Algebra_Ops/dot.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Linear_Algebra_Ops/dot.md:4
msgid ""
"简介：对两个tensor进行矩阵乘操作。tensor需要是二维或三维并且维度需一致。对于三维块，tl.dot执行批量矩阵乘法，其中每个块的第一维代表批量维度。\n"
"原型：\n"
msgstr ""
"Introduction: Performs matrix multiplication on two tensors. The tensors must be two-dimensional or three-dimensional and have consistent dimensions. For three-dimensional blocks, `tl.dot` performs batched matrix multiplication, where the first dimension of each block represents the batch dimension.  \n"
"Prototype:\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Linear_Algebra_Ops/dot.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.dot(input, other, acc=None, input_precision=None, allow_tf32=None, max_num_imprecise_acc=None, out_dtype=triton.language.float32, _semantic=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Linear_Algebra_Ops/dot.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Linear_Algebra_Ops/dot.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Linear_Algebra_Ops/dot.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `input`        | `int8 fp16 bf16 fp32`     |     第一个输入，2D or 3D 张量， 为了避免溢出 取值范围限制为-5-5     |\n"
"| `other`       | `int8 fp16 bf16 fp32`     |     第二个输入,  2D or 3D 张量，为了避免溢出 取值范围限制为-5-5    |\n"
"| `acc`           | `int32  float32`    | 存累加结果的张量, accumulator tensor. If not None, the result is added to this tensor, acc_dtype支持 {:code:`float16`, :code:`float32`, :code:`int32`} |\n"
"| `input_precision`   | -                 |  Available options for NVIDIA 通过选择精度模式来决定是否启用 Tensor Cores 加速    |\n"
"| `max_num_imprecise_acc`     | `int`    | 多少次低精度的累加数（当前昇腾不支持低精度累加） |\n"
"| `out_dtype`     | `fp32  int32`    | 输出结果类型|\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `input` | `int8 fp16 bf16 fp32` | First input, 2D or 3D tensor. To avoid overflow, the value range is limited to -5 to 5 |\n"
"| `other` | `int8 fp16 bf16 fp32` | Second input, 2D or 3D tensor. To avoid overflow, the value range is limited to -5 to 5 |\n"
"| `acc` | `int32 float32` | Tensor storing accumulation results. If not None, the result is added to this tensor. `acc_dtype` supports {:code:`float16`, :code:`float32`, :code:`int32`} |\n"
"| `input_precision` | - | Available options for NVIDIA. Select the precision mode to enable Tensor Cores acceleration |\n"
"| `max_num_imprecise_acc` | `int` | Number of low-precision accumulations (currently Ascend does not support low-precision accumulation) |\n"
"| `out_dtype` | `fp32 int32` | Output result type |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Linear_Algebra_Ops/dot.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tl.tensor`：矩阵乘结果\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tl.tensor`: matrix multiplication result\n"

